## Exercise 8: Password Aging Management (chage)

### View Current Password Aging Information

```bash
chage -l newuser
```

---

### Set Minimum Days

```bash
chage -m 3 newuser
```

Verify:

```bash
chage -l newuser
```

---

### Set Maximum Days

```bash
chage -M 60 newuser
```

Verify:

```bash
chage -l newuser
```

---

### Set Warning Days

```bash
chage -W 3 newuser
```

Verify:

```bash
chage -l newuser
```

---

### Set Inactive Days

```bash
chage -I 7 newuser
```

Verify:

```bash
chage -l newuser
```

---

### Set Password Expiry Date

```bash
chage -E 2027-01-01 newuser
```

Verify:

```bash
chage -l newuser
```

